Package: ggtwotone
Type: Package
Title: Dual-Tone and Contrast-Aware ggplot2 Geoms
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Beenu", "Sareena",
      email = "beenusareena810@gmail.com",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Description: Provides dual-stroke and contrast-aware extensions to 'ggplot2', 
    designed for improved visibility and accessibility in complex visualizations. 
    Includes geoms for dual-stroke segments, regression lines, curved annotations, 
    function plots, and adaptive text: 'geom_segment_dual', 'geom_lm_dual', 
    'geom_curve_dual', 'geom_curve_dual_function', and 'geom_text_contrast'. 
    Also includes a utility function 'adjust_contrast_pair()' for computing 
    perceptually distinct color pairs using WCAG or APCA contrast standards.
